INSERT INTO external_providers (pubkey, name, domain, website_url, data_source, created_at_ns)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
               ON CONFLICT(pubkey) DO UPDATE SET
                   name = excluded.name,
                   domain = excluded.domain,
                   website_url = excluded.website_url,
                   data_source = excluded.data_source
